Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you sell cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't carry them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, before?\NBy the tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was performing a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... sorry I intruded then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still spiraling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a dark, lonely feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought maybe you could rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow, I still feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm moved by the scent of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for those smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The simple act of pursuing her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having reached an impasse\Nin my work and in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sought to acquaint myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with everyday ennui,\Nsired by apathy and restlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever-fleeing the authenticity\Nof my own experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was entirely spent by a life, \Ncomposed of accumulated fictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are you always alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be alone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know today's date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you perform your ritual today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It will make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When my wish comes true,\NI can disappear completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappear, leaving nothing\Nin the world behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to keep\Nperforming the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, the red umbrella protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what's tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you follow me,\Nthat first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... because you intrigue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My unsound heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the consuming loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of longing for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps anyone will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will love me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}constantly, ceaselessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Is this true love?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I feel at ease with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We're compatible."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ponder such ideas everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad and Mom are sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everybody's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sickest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's stood there before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I felt strange. {I merged this and the last line into one sentence in my previous version, but I am not so sure about that anymore. Thoughts?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Do I look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only my favorite things are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Including me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.\NYou're one of the gang. {Going to need the eldon TLC on this one. JP -> IT -> EN is certainly a pipeline}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I like coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She never listened to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, \Nor you'll end up like your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you share that man's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!\NWhere are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the phone and call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked myself\Nto the bone to raise you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At least your sister had a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep up this selfish behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You, you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you talk to me that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father tortured me,\Ndoing whatever he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now my own daughter {line break?}hates me this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of living...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get out of the hospital tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's your birthday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Won't you come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NSo let's play together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone\Non my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainy days are days\Nfor my father and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow's my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the truth is only an enemy that wounds her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days of her life pass in\Nloneliness, a darkness without exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I longed to ease her sadness\Nand anxiety, if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if only to atone\Nfor my own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,5:59 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,50 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,6 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,6 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,give you a tour of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret fourth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,first floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absolutely secret!\NYou can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,fifth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sixth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,seventh floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they all secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These... stairs...\NI'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting old...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You like high places?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I come here to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Check what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The light is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,everything's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better if I didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How about my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I'm still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Still okay to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A blank-faced mosquito falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge mosquito,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,much, much bigger than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It slumps and is still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A much larger creature caught it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and took flight, the mosquito in its grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew up and passed right over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it released its grasp\N and the mosquito fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It drifted down, down, down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an interesting head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk. {TLC / TODO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything. I want to hear you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know FireMan? {I've seen people capitalize it like this but I feel like "Fireman" would be more correct no?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he was like UltraMan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His enemies attack him\Nand in the end, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,FireMan ends up burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He yells "Fire!" but\Nactually he's afraid of fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's FireMan 'cause he burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,\Nbut it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what she says,\Nbut I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, all she wanted was\Nto hear someone's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, all she wanted was\Nto stop feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Echoes from the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}creaking arcade roof opening\Nand an all too ordinary sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}disturbed my ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You like cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as much as boats and trains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I like 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my big sister did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was back at the hotel\Ngetting my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean where\Nwere you 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I took my usual route here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the bookstore, department store,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the toy store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean where were you\Nbefore you came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I wanted to think things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kind of tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, it was all about nothing. {TODO}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother always said\Nlife is full of tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.01,0:24:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.30,0:24:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No phone calls today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.43,0:24:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the deal's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.10,0:24:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:25:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My usual work exhausts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.78,0:25:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm keeping my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to\Nmake live action films, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.54,0:25:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Live action films... films.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.75,0:25:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Films?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Films...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.21,0:25:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's stopping you? You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.51,0:25:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you're "Director".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.64,0:25:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.81,0:25:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.94,0:25:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.69,0:25:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want blue, the blue one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.65,0:25:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This? This blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.65,0:25:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.47,0:25:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:26:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.13,0:26:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?\NTomorrow's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.85,0:26:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.36,0:26:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.16,0:26:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still okay today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.44,0:27:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I start shooting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.95,0:27:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.24,0:27:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.95,0:27:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An outline by...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.88,0:27:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Reel 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.76,0:27:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.18,0:27:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.93,0:27:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shooting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.94,0:27:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.70,0:27:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.62,0:28:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my outfit look alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.96,0:28:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.92,0:28:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I think it looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.46,0:28:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about clothes. {alt: costumes}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.18,0:28:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.85,0:28:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.65,0:28:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.36,0:28:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.21,0:28:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.88,0:28:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.55,0:29:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy on the train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.87,0:29:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.49,0:29:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The streetcar is a perfect means of escape \Nfrom the tedium of my days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.50,0:29:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scenery flows by cinematically.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.58,0:29:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound effects are punctual. {TODO: Retime}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.54,0:29:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My fantasy about her expands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.89,0:29:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be bored for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.26,0:29:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our idle routine, the days \NI spend with her, like a lukewarm bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.89,0:29:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}her faint smile seems to agree with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.35,0:29:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day, a countdown towards death.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.94,0:29:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dare not risk negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.81,0:29:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the more reason to film her, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Images, especially animation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}simply embody our\Npersonal and collective fantasies,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.37,0:30:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}manipulating selected information,\Nand fictional constructs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.25,0:30:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in live-action film, \Nrecording actuality, does not correspond to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.88,0:30:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conversely, reality, \Nco-opted by fiction, loses its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.92,0:30:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The inversion of reality and fiction."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.30,0:30:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of this matters to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.76,0:30:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My consciousness, my reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.93,0:30:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my subject, all converge in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.58,0:30:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly, she longs to escape into fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.02,0:30:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly, I long to escape from fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.03,0:30:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to keep a visual record\Nof these contradictory phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.65,0:30:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, my behavior is really\Nno more than an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.24,0:30:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for my inability to communicate\Nexcept through images.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.63,0:30:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way to the mystery basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.42,0:31:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No trespassing\Nbecause the camera is prohibited,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.97,0:31:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot show you anymore. My apologies {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.35,0:31:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.52,0:31:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,force me to omit the first \Nthrough seventh floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.53,0:31:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.75,0:31:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.59,0:31:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's high...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.05,0:31:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where she always checks herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.43,0:31:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.02,0:31:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.02,0:31:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day, she postpones tomorrow,\Nby transforming today into yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.32,0:32:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A typical day in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never goes to sleep before dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she awakens before 6 AM\Nto dial and listen to the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.25,0:32:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As far as I can tell,\Nshe hardly sleeps at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.31,0:32:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.60,0:32:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.73,0:32:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you sleepy?\NDon't you want to sleep? {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.15,0:32:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I close my eyes to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.99,0:32:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,something really heavy \Nseems to crush my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I push it away and away and away,\Nbut it keeps bearing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.58,0:32:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't avert my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.55,0:33:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.92,0:33:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.09,0:33:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like tomorrow coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.80,0:33:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.85,0:33:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.10,0:33:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.07,0:33:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Terrified to face the truth,\Nshe rejects even sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.61,0:33:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that there is actual truth\N in the ambiguity of human memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.12,0:33:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her best and only means\Nof survival depends on her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.92,0:33:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destruction and renewal of memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.33,0:33:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly many more days bear\Nforgetting than joyful commemoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.67,0:33:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it that I want from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.42,0:33:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get some sleep.\NYou're shooting again tomorrow... {TODO: Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.40,0:34:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again, today, I record her image.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.07,0:34:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I find in the act\Nof capturing her being,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.78,0:34:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}according to my own will, \Nfor my own purpose, relief from my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Images transform my real past into fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.70,0:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of us edits and alters our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By giving form and existence\Nto this process through images,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.63,0:34:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I reinvent my past, whitewashing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.47,0:34:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}into an idealized history.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Re-creating the present\Nas something invulnerable,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.56,0:34:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as a world of fiction and fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.93,0:34:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the same, only differing in our methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.62,0:34:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.29,0:35:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.71,0:35:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.46,0:35:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.67,0:35:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.05,0:35:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.72,0:35:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I read the softer stuff. {Folded under ZERO pressure}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.89,0:35:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do read it. Disgusting. {Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Playboy, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.82,0:35:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Females drowning in their lust,\Ncoming wherever they please..."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.45,0:35:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Normal sex doesn't do it"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.07,0:35:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.95,0:35:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"The nymphomaniacs who\Nlust for kinky settings"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.33,0:35:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.\NIt's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.21,0:35:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.14,0:35:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You like this stuff too. {boob} {Should this be a question mark?}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.10,0:36:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.10,0:36:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, "vavoom".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.94,0:36:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.82,0:36:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.74,0:36:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.83,0:36:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.63,0:36:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.51,0:36:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all men like sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.60,0:36:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.14,0:36:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Director \Nneither likes nor dislikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.85,0:36:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't dislike it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.64,0:36:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.98,0:36:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.82,0:36:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause if you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.28,0:36:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no more\Nthan male and female.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.82,0:36:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.28,0:37:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.51,0:37:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.91,0:37:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kumoha 42 street car.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.54,0:37:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The type: \N20 meters with driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.21,0:37:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Two doors and benches on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Semi-cross seats\Nperpendicular to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.17,0:37:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Street car color: \NGrape #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.43,0:37:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Capacity of 104,\N68 sitting, 36 standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight: 45 tons.\NBuilt in 1933. {Split}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.81,0:37:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These two cars are the only ones\Nof this type still operating in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.53,0:37:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.92,0:37:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.54,0:37:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in Ube.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.42,0:37:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.93,0:38:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell whether it's any good or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.68,0:38:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll email you an outline when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.81,0:38:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.56,0:38:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds good. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.07,0:38:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a woman again, Dirty Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.58,0:38:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.12,0:38:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At least once a day\Nyou get to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.58,0:38:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.58,0:38:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who it is.\NAt least someone calls you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.43,0:38:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.61,0:38:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:38:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.12,0:39:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That night,\Nher smile disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.74,0:39:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with the falling rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.32,0:39:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.41,0:39:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.55,0:40:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.63,0:40:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.43,0:41:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.45,0:41:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.13,0:42:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.63,0:42:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my father and sister's day!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.76,0:42:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I like rainy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.63,0:42:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because when it rains,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.85,0:42:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all the merry people in the world\Nfinally walk with their eyes downcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.31,0:42:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I like rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.19,0:42:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.49,0:42:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What she keeps bottled up on sunny days,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.32,0:42:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}flows as from a broken darn when it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.49,0:42:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her feelings of loneliness and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.12,0:42:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These emotions elevate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.84,0:42:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}preventing her from \Nengaging in a certain behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.22,0:42:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.51,0:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}engendering her complex reactions\Nto the phenomenon called rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.68,0:42:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the sadness that she harbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.68,0:43:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt the deaths in her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.19,0:43:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this moment, I acknowledge yet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.19,0:43:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that in her heart, she yearns
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to cease existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A brand new
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.66,0:43:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,morning's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.12,0:43:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A morning of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your heart with joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.66,0:43:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.54,0:43:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your vibrant heart
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.30,0:43:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the song on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.30,0:43:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fragrant breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.56,0:43:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, 1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.52,0:43:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.74,0:43:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Having something to hold onto\Nwhen you're scared
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.95,0:43:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is good enough in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.95,0:44:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.54,0:44:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,secret
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.08,0:44:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ritual space.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.66,0:44:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It always has to be flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.88,0:44:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.93,0:44:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But as of today, it's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.14,0:44:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director can come and go.\NVideocamera okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.77,0:44:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.23,0:44:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.78,0:44:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.61,0:44:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.08,0:44:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.41,0:44:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.29,0:44:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.27,0:44:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A videocamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.13,0:44:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Matching.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.63,0:44:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.05,0:45:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A hesitant reply isn't a good sign, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.31,0:45:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.35,0:45:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A favorite place?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.65,0:45:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorite place...\NThis sort of place isn't bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.07,0:45:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.74,0:45:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.16,0:45:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.83,0:45:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple place with only sand and sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.33,0:45:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.67,0:45:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was beautiful\Nbecause it was unpopulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.30,0:45:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No humans there to warp it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful world\Nwithout people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.35,0:45:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.10,0:45:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Like railroad tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.14,0:45:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.35,0:45:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.23,0:45:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.52,0:45:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How shall I put it...\NBecause they are mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.41,0:46:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then rails are fixed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.14,0:46:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you ride them,\Nyou needn't choose a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.14,0:46:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.63,0:46:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.21,0:46:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.50,0:46:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.92,0:46:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these two rails
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.55,0:46:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,will never come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.84,0:46:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.68,0:46:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the two are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.97,0:46:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.09,0:46:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.76,0:46:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abused and then abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.34,0:46:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.57,0:46:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my fear made me tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.57,0:46:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magical powers\Nof a pair of dice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.45,0:46:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}still sway me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.18,0:46:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}undiminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.25,0:46:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only one day I could say
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.54,0:46:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.17,0:46:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hum to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.35,0:47:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My umbrella!\NMy umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.80,0:47:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I died in your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.09,0:47:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the skies part?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.97,0:47:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the wind flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.43,0:47:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beneath the steps of that dark red space
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.98,0:47:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you used that sharp stick
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.66,0:48:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and struck my bursting...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.24,0:48:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.45,0:48:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, I can't write.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.83,0:48:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.25,0:48:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe time to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.84,0:48:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do if I quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.47,0:48:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.60,0:48:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.56,0:48:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.84,0:49:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, she didn't\Nventure near the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.46,0:49:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or to the railroad tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.55,0:49:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never attempted\Nto leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.29,0:50:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.29,0:50:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.54,0:50:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.18,0:50:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.98,0:50:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never discussed what frightened her,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.06,0:50:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what she wanted to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.85,0:50:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She no longer saw anyone but herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.40,0:50:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer exist inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.37,0:50:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day passed without us\Nexchanging a single word,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.29,0:51:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a single glance, \Nor lifting the camera to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.00,0:51:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For I hadn't the courage\Nto capture her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.55,0:51:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her unrelenting, oppressive reality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.72,0:51:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}began to bear down on me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.70,0:51:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbeknownst to me, \Nshe had found a cat that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.38,0:51:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look mother,\Nisn't this cat cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.38,0:51:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.72,0:51:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's mother, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.38,0:51:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our very, very kind mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.25,0:51:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say hello to her, Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.85,0:52:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.40,0:52:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.77,0:52:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.28,0:52:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her ritual remained interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.02,0:52:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since that day, she hadn't climbed\Nto the roof, or visited the tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.25,0:52:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but played with the cat all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.08,0:52:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playing with the cat seemed to\Nallow her to avoid herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.45,0:52:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She still slept rarely,\Nand now barely ate,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.89,0:52:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}only played with the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.64,0:52:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing else worth\Nrecording took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.48,0:52:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except that of course we neither\Nspoke nor exchanged a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.88,0:52:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remained locked outside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.44,0:52:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.29,0:53:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.25,0:53:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat slipped away that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.31,0:53:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The photographer's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.56,0:53:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The writer's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.01,0:53:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The director's obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.73,0:53:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The actor's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.82,0:53:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Red cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.57,0:53:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swelling lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.49,0:53:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tightened strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.41,0:53:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human heart is fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.62,0:53:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is easily captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.12,0:53:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An evil song,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.71,0:53:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}drifting through the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.00,0:53:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}envelopes the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.92,0:53:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.92,0:53:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Announcing,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.67,0:53:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My true mother has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.13,0:53:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl dances
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.68,0:54:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wildly, wildly
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.19,0:54:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wildly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.57,0:54:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never did come home that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.90,0:55:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.36,0:55:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I noticed that I was somewhat\Nrelieved the cat had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.11,0:55:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.95,0:55:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.63,0:55:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.42,0:55:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.93,0:56:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.72,0:56:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.35,0:56:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.50,0:57:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.88,0:57:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.84,0:57:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why weren't you\Nwith me then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.31,0:57:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.99,0:57:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.22,0:57:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.96,0:58:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.42,0:58:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beating away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.60,0:58:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A gentle sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.85,0:58:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.50,0:59:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.84,0:59:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappear like that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.51,0:59:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever leave me alone again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.69,0:59:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.77,0:59:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.99,0:59:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.91,0:59:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.66,1:00:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with me on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.79,1:00:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.73,1:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.74,1:00:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.41,1:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.87,1:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wake up!\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.92,1:01:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's past 6!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.22,1:01:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No... hold on...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.14,1:01:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.44,1:01:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.17,1:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.85,1:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.53,1:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart says I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.87,1:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There there...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.08,1:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Which line today?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.91,1:02:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.80,1:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.23,1:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's someone scary!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.48,1:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Director! Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.24,1:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeys and goats!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.42,1:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a huge discovery this morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.84,1:03:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.26,1:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared to fall asleep anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.09,1:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you were with me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.10,1:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I could close my eyes just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.19,1:03:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And like,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.98,1:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.02,1:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing came crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.41,1:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my body felt really light.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.20,1:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.29,1:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.37,1:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really amazing!\NDo you understand what this means?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.92,1:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing discovery!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.30,1:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.35,1:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Great angle.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.94,1:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's not so bad when I lie like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.48,1:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.21,1:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuddling is nice, isn't it? I like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.01,1:04:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.84,1:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, I like this better
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.17,1:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.11,1:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.26,1:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.14,1:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, well then,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.34,1:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you like about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.85,1:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.70,1:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.23,1:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.31,1:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when I wake up in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.84,1:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beside me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.95,1:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.61,1:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so reassuring.\NAmazing, isn't it? {Split maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.04,1:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.35,1:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mouth's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.57,1:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,always wide open,m, and you drool.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.21,1:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You... fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.59,1:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.64,1:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it over?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.60,1:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All these used tires
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.60,1:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,look like people's ripped off teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.82,1:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me shoot too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.24,1:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? I want to shoot, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.58,1:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't be my film anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.79,1:06:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me, let me!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.25,1:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This okay? Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.09,1:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.26,1:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.55,1:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.56,1:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.27,1:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.14,1:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.90,1:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.86,1:06:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look upset?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.19,1:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.15,1:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.24,1:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.75,1:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been tired lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.46,1:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.42,1:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.25,1:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.34,1:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to baby you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.64,1:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.18,1:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good boy, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.36,1:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll baby you more.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.49,1:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you mother me then?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.49,1:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.12,1:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Piggyback?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.41,1:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.58,1:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.17,1:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A two-shot!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.93,1:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.18,1:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.44,1:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.95,1:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.24,1:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.45,1:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.03,1:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.70,1:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.89,1:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.91,1:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nearly a month since I met her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.75,1:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fed up with the endless "yesterdays",
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.00,1:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and lulled by the "todays."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.38,1:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anxious, too, that tomorrow may bring change,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.47,1:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet eagerly awaiting the change it may finally bring.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.35,1:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I want from this reality I share with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.02,1:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The constancy of the past or the change of the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.69,1:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.11,1:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these were no more than idle doubts that shifted with my moods.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.25,1:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You snore every night, just like a hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.67,1:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These days will come to an end.\NEventually, I'll part with her. {Split}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.84,1:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even my life will end one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.18,1:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the more reason to treasure\Nthese slight, fleeting emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.06,1:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the excess of boredom and intimacy
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.65,1:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were simply exhausting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.57,1:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I realized that gradually,\Nthe times that being with her depressed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.99,1:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}outstripped the times that I enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.15,1:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday that'll happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.20,1:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, today,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.75,1:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there was this blue car
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.25,1:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of the shrine,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.19,1:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and this car, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.67,1:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was really cute...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.01,1:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening?\NYou paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.22,1:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.39,1:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.15,1:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.09,1:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He hates me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.80,1:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.02,1:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He hates me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.06,1:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hates me, hates me, hates me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.27,1:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be left alone again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.15,1:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be left alone again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.65,1:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.86,1:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abused and then abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.03,1:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried everything
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.16,1:13:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my fear made me tremble.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.00,1:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magical powers of a pair of dice...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.13,1:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...still sway me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.59,1:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only one day I could say,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.84,1:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm so glad I met you."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.68,1:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hum to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.23,1:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, your sister...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.44,1:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.11,1:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She never listened to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.74,1:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets now!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.90,1:13:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, or you'll\Nend up like your sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.83,1:13:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you share\Nthat man's blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.12,1:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.38,1:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.67,1:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with that man again!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.62,1:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.47,1:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, clueless!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.18,1:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so patronizing!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.39,1:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All you ever want is\Nfor me to be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.23,1:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Always, always, always.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.85,1:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just patronizing me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.62,1:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have a clue
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.65,1:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is I really want! Not a clue!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.24,1:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.45,1:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You only remember what you gave me,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.29,1:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but not how you mistreated me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.50,1:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.38,1:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what, we're even for all your troubles?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.92,1:14:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and die!\NI won't care! {Split}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.97,1:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.60,1:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you nice to me then?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.88,1:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.07,1:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.70,1:15:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.96,1:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her heart is overcome by a world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.00,1:16:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}awash in cruelty, harshness,\Nhatred and loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.51,1:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that is the way of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.80,1:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of us fears its absurdity, and curses it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.55,1:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, the world is immeasurably vast,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.77,1:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gentleness, mercy and\Nempathy linger in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.61,1:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I desperately wanted her
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.44,1:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to know this reality as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.53,1:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.50,1:16:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.54,1:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.43,1:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But her heart is so delicate and vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.06,1:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I really capable of embracing
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.56,1:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the endless darkness inside it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.21,1:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I'm incapable of accepting her...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.40,1:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I find myself enveloped\Nin an anxiety I cannot shake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.11,1:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, again, I can do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.78,1:17:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}6 in the morning,\Nshe's back to her usual self
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.78,1:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's returned to her little world
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.09,1:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}constructed entirely
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.59,1:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of her protections, denying the existence
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.93,1:17:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of whatever can harm her.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.22,1:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except now she has chosen to rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.89,1:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it always sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.23,1:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She begins another day of life,\Nbrimming with fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.94,1:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}plastered in self-deception,\Nsealed by oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My own faint panic,\N"I've got to do something"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.58,1:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is futilely idle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.66,1:18:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.12,1:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, just working.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.17,1:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside then.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.97,1:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot your movie,\Nthat's your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.89,1:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that work?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.22,1:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.47,1:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Japan today, all forms of expression,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.82,1:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}beginning with images, serve only
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.28,1:18:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as either
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.45,1:18:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}time-killing entertainment\Nfor those without occupation,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.16,1:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or as momentary respite \Nfor those who are afraid of pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.00,1:18:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People desire either real scandals\Namplified by rawness,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.85,1:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.17,1:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the illusion of beautifully adapted fictions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.40,1:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is true of me. {What does this mean???}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.22,1:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to create appropriate relationships,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.89,1:19:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I escape into a fictional world,\Nconstructed on a fantasy of daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.87,1:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even this film, when completed,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.19,1:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will become a device to deliver\Na certain amount of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.40,1:19:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devoid of surprises,\Nand a measure of time spent in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.66,1:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wants images beyond that?\NWho needs them?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.01,1:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By then, I had abandoned\Nher as a visual construct.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to film anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.88,1:19:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as she was present,\NI didn't need to make a film.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.94,1:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had always been entranced with the idea of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.14,1:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}being madly loved, and loving madly.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.39,1:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet this was a stupendous burden, exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.67,1:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could I really bear it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.40,1:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.53,1:20:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came back!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.93,1:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.14,1:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.56,1:20:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.78,1:20:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.66,1:20:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.45,1:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait! Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.96,1:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back,\NI know you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.50,1:20:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You do, right!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.17,1:21:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not my sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.48,1:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.79,1:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse—
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.74,1:22:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.23,1:22:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.48,1:22:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.24,1:22:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A reunion? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.78,1:22:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to his triumphant return!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.45,1:22:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.58,1:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.74,1:23:45.50,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: The following song has never been translated into English, \Nand we could not find someone to translate it in time for this release. \N\NWe apologize for the inconvenience. \N\N - Heartside <3 {Might not include at all tbh}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.84,1:25:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.47,1:26:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.60,1:26:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.64,1:26:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With some woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.77,1:26:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.23,1:26:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out drinking\Nwith my old friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.99,1:26:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.78,1:26:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.78,1:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.04,1:26:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.79,1:26:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.00,1:26:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.76,1:26:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.45,1:26:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but your heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.30,1:27:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever kissed someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.34,1:27:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.39,1:27:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.60,1:27:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.32,1:27:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.03,1:27:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.20,1:27:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.87,1:27:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.05,1:28:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to have sex?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.89,1:28:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have sex with you,\Nwill you stay forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.61,1:28:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.78,1:28:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better than cuddling.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.74,1:28:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just put up with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.54,1:28:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see \Nand touch my breasts, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.04,1:28:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, have sex with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.38,1:28:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.05,1:28:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.43,1:28:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.85,1:28:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.23,1:28:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start hating me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.07,1:29:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.34,1:29:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.84,1:29:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this,\NI will become my sister...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.97,1:29:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become my sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.02,1:29:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... Still...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.07,1:29:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I died in your place.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.40,1:29:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the skies part.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.99,1:29:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would the wind flow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.66,1:29:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beneath the steps of that dark red space
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.25,1:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you used that sharpened stick
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.02,1:30:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.05,1:30:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}striking my
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.56,1:30:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}quivering lips
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.48,1:30:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}swollen to bursting
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.18,1:30:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tasting
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.52,1:30:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of sorrow and betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.03,1:30:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That song
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.61,1:30:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.20,1:30:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I peer back again and again
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.14,1:30:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at that dreamlike state.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.25,1:30:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.\NSorry, I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.06,1:31:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.61,1:31:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How unusual. Calling at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.86,1:31:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat got your tongue?\NHello, hello...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.14,1:31:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.65,1:31:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.50,1:32:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You read this?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.59,1:32:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.13,1:32:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.13,1:32:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.38,1:32:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.64,1:32:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you have to?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.48,1:32:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with me because\Nyou have to be for work?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.07,1:32:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.49,1:32:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my father?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.24,1:32:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.45,1:32:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.67,1:32:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.78,1:32:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I worthless?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.80,1:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.01,1:32:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going away?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.98,1:33:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.86,1:33:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.82,1:33:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just tempted when \Nshe called you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.82,1:33:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What woman? She's nobody...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.70,1:33:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.80,1:33:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.47,1:33:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear your heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.19,1:33:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.99,1:33:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Two answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.78,1:34:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Three answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.96,1:34:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How many answers?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.88,1:34:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.23,1:34:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By 6 that morning, she had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.78,1:34:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of my sister's?\NYou dating her?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.29,1:34:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.58,1:34:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... That girl got a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.13,1:34:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.97,1:34:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought she'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.34,1:35:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her sister appeared instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.14,1:35:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, she'd rejected even herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.94,1:35:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of my business,\Nbut be nice to her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.98,1:35:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nshe always liked this kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.74,1:35:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.33,1:35:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parents split up \Nwhen she was young,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.79,1:35:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Father walked out on both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.91,1:35:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wound up dead with the new woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.29,1:35:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it rain on that day?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.34,1:35:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, went ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.17,1:35:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.92,1:35:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.97,1:35:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And, your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.48,1:35:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A streetcar hit her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.23,1:35:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,On her birthday, she'd always cry,\N"Why did they leave me?"
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.00,1:35:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mother was a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.45,1:36:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She blamed anything bad on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.18,1:36:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Dad's fault,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.54,1:36:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that woman's fault,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.54,1:36:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my sister's fault, my fault,\Nthe world's fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.13,1:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It never occurred to her\Nthe fault might be hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.55,1:36:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor sister.\NShe was always compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.89,1:36:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She only heard nagging, \N"Why can't you be like your sister?"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.87,1:36:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like she was no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.60,1:36:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.02,1:36:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she'll\Never learn to like herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.79,1:36:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone I'd like to see. You coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.76,1:37:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business, butt out.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.72,1:37:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.86,1:37:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,New guy, huh...\NMust run in the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.58,1:37:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.42,1:37:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You only show up when it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.04,1:37:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that face?\NSame as last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.76,1:37:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seen my cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.39,1:37:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.98,1:38:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My cat, my cat,\Nyou know, Jam.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.11,1:38:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No I don't.\NHow the hell would I know?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.27,1:38:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar, liar, liar...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.74,1:38:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You deny attacking my little sister, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.33,1:38:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou are her, not her sister. {???}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.42,1:38:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.37,1:38:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister went away a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.48,1:38:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You ranted about killing her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.59,1:38:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I say I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.76,1:38:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were babbling some crap\Nabout how you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.68,1:38:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.36,1:38:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this to me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.32,1:38:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask me to let you stay\N'cause you got nowhere else,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.91,1:38:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then you split.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.45,1:38:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's about some cat!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.79,1:38:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You come wandering back\Nranting about a cat!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.00,1:39:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.71,1:39:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.43,1:39:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.93,1:39:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After all I did for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.56,1:39:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.06,1:39:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.74,1:39:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.75,1:39:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.42,1:39:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.46,1:39:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.47,1:39:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.60,1:40:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with you makes me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.65,1:40:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Drives me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.28,1:40:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.07,1:40:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are demented!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.29,1:40:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna be like your sister?\NWell you already are.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.63,1:40:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep around, get knocked up,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.21,1:40:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,spitting image of that sister you love!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.51,1:40:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.77,1:40:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.52,1:40:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.32,1:40:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.28,1:40:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.29,1:41:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.88,1:41:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.92,1:41:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you pulling the same,\N"Go away" crap on him?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.43,1:41:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.51,1:41:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister! Sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.43,1:41:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister used to say...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.02,1:41:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"My own sister scares me."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.40,1:41:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!\NDon't!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.69,1:41:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always have to be\Nso damn dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.03,1:41:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.\NGive me back the ring, the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.41,1:41:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.20,1:41:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.16,1:41:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you\N"All I did for you" me!? {Man this entire section is messed up. I have zero idea what this even refers to}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.34,1:41:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You never did a thing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.80,1:41:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister did everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.87,1:41:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.84,1:41:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with you!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.26,1:42:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.73,1:42:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out! You!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.69,1:42:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.56,1:42:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back the ring!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.07,1:42:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you callin' stupid?!\NWho doesn't get it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.58,1:42:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.25,1:42:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.38,1:42:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.64,1:42:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.34,1:42:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my life!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.35,1:42:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.99,1:43:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, why were\Nyou with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.62,1:43:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.54,1:43:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After you disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.48,1:43:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he came after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.30,1:44:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to go away?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.81,1:44:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.48,1:44:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretended to like me,\Nbut you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.36,1:44:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So God punished you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.78,1:44:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.\NBe happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.54,1:44:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.73,1:46:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.86,1:47:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.\NBe happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.65,1:47:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.51,1:47:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.60,1:47:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.40,1:47:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.31,1:47:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.53,1:47:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.57,1:47:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.95,1:47:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true,\N'cause she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.92,1:48:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.46,1:48:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming to see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.42,1:48:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.16,1:48:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know...\NMaybe she's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.14,1:48:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.25,1:48:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.90,1:48:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She calls you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.57,1:48:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you answer my phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.61,1:48:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep out of my business!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.83,1:48:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut it's what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.79,1:48:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.12,1:48:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.29,1:48:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.80,1:48:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!\NYou go away, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.47,1:48:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.47,1:48:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.47,1:48:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You run away from everything\Nyou don't like, and wind up
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.31,1:49:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own little world.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.27,1:49:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.02,1:49:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You just deny anything you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.48,1:49:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.44,1:49:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you want everyone to go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.95,1:49:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NCut the crap! You depress me!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.55,1:49:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?\NI told you to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.27,1:49:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.19,1:49:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.36,1:49:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.20,1:49:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,like...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.08,1:50:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.87,1:50:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.84,1:50:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.\NI like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.76,1:50:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying just like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.80,1:50:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.06,1:50:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.27,1:50:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.73,1:50:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.74,1:50:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.96,1:50:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.42,1:50:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.02,1:51:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.28,1:51:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, my mother cursed my father
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.12,1:51:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to drive him away.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.87,1:51:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's curse came to pass
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.58,1:51:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father left.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.50,1:51:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried hard
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.69,1:51:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep her from driving me away.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.97,1:51:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But she told me,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.45,1:51:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she never told my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.71,1:51:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.81,1:51:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A red umbrella and red shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.57,1:51:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother bought them for me\Nwhen we went shopping together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.33,1:52:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The first things that weren't\Nmy sisters hand-me-downs.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.50,1:52:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They matched my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.29,1:52:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But my mother threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.17,1:52:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She called them old.\NSaid she didn't need them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.33,1:52:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.43,1:52:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd do that to me one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.64,1:52:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of being alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.29,1:52:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm scared of mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.94,1:52:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I cursed everyone to drive them away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.23,1:52:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse will come to pass on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.16,1:52:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So my birthday always has to be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.25,1:52:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But mother didn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.50,1:52:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to kill her\Nin my head, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.26,1:53:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.55,1:53:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I had to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.22,1:53:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I began dressing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.64,1:53:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.31,1:53:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,would bring my
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.90,1:53:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,new and happy life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.74,1:53:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.42,1:53:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.09,1:53:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.06,1:53:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All we really know
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.76,1:53:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is that tomorrow we'll still be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.56,1:53:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.52,1:54:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to try to see your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.41,1:54:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.88,1:54:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.63,1:54:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.13,1:54:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.55,1:54:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.56,1:54:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own mother? Leaving you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.81,1:54:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.69,1:54:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you alone for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.65,1:54:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I leave you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.66,1:54:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When did your mother leave you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.37,1:54:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.75,1:55:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you always left me alone...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.72,1:55:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You only cared for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.32,1:55:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.95,1:55:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did her sister pass away?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.54,1:55:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.71,1:55:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We are apart, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.76,1:55:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She worries about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.64,1:55:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She called me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.35,1:56:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd been out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.03,1:56:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.74,1:56:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.66,1:56:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so busy thinking...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.50,1:56:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about myself, that maybe\NI didn't think about your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.76,1:56:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was difficult for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.56,1:56:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.19,1:56:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Always complaining, always getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.15,1:56:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I never did anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.53,1:56:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I only...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.78,1:56:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.66,1:57:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I couldn't really love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.34,1:57:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.35,1:57:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.56,1:57:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.94,1:57:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's selfish...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.74,1:57:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.87,1:57:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's selfish of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.79,1:57:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about when I was lonely?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.30,1:57:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What about all those\Nyears when I was alone?!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.84,1:57:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All those...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.59,1:57:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't have cared less\Nwhen I needed your love,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.85,1:58:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you're lonely,\Nyou come to get me!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.77,1:58:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.90,1:58:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What! After all this time,\Nnow you're lonely!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.11,1:58:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.32,1:58:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.53,1:58:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.16,1:58:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was lonely,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.71,1:58:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you just ignored me...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.17,1:58:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.05,1:58:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!\NI'm asking you, go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.42,1:58:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go... Just go...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.59,1:58:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go away, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.22,1:58:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.56,1:58:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.06,1:58:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.80,1:58:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.40,1:58:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, won't you come home?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.78,1:59:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come home just once? Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.66,1:59:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.92,1:59:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come home...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.59,1:59:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.35,1:59:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.24,1:59:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up from your dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.29,1:59:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this part of your dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.67,1:59:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we still dreaming a dream?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.60,2:00:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is our reality...\NYour reality.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.00,2:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday
