Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.45,2:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.78,2:01:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,please smile.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.99,2:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
